This is a template to display the characteristics of a Belgian Municipality.

==使用==
<pre>{{Infobox Belgium municipality
| name               = 
| native_name        = 
| native_name_lang   = 
| namefr             = 
| namenl             = 
| namede             = 
| picture            = 
| picture-legend     = 
| imagesize          = 
| map                = 
| arms               = 
| flag               = 
| map_dot_label      = 
| coordinates        = {{Coord}}
| nis                = 
| arrondissement     = 
| list_of_mayors     = 
| mayor              = 
| majority           = 
| population_demonym = 
| population_metro   = 
| postal-codes       = 
| telephone-area     = 
| web                = 
| footnotes          = 
}}</pre>

* <code>nis</code> = number identifying each Belgian municipality in Directorate-general [[Statistics Belgium]] [http://www.statbel.fgov.be/]; This number is used to retrieve data (population statistics, coordinates, economy data) from three subtemplates. 
* For <code>region</code>, <code>community</code> and <code>province</code> you can use templates (see below), and else they are displayed based on the given NIS number.
* Fhe coordinates (lat_deg etc.) are needed for the dot on the map of Belgium and the title coordinates.

